title: Gypsy Den
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Electic coffee house located at The Lab across from the camp in Costa Mesa. Casual and artsy space. Serves breakfast until 11:30am. Veg food options include bean burger, vegetarian chili, vegetable lasagna, and other American fare. Soy based bacon and sausage links. Some food is pre-made in the morning and warmed up for you when you order it.
